author: Rosenthol Curtis
title: Austin Musicial Duo UntamedClick Release New Single “Thousand Miles"
text:
Today Coast 2 Coast Mixtapes announces the release of “Thousand Miles", the latest single by Austin-based recording artists, UntamedClick. The single is currently available for streaming and download at the official Coast 2 Coast Mixtapes website . UntamedClick is currently seeking press opportunities, interviews, features, and more. They can be reached through their official Twitter page .
About UntamedClick: UntamedClick is a rap duo consisting of Mike Ceezy and Southside Fresh. Based out of Austin, TX, both artists have been working together since 2003. Reminiscent of fellow Texas-natives and Hip-Hop icons UGK, UntamedClick's music is meant to express real life experiences of life husling through the streets of Austin. Mike Ceezy has a unique style and is versatile, sharing personal experiences about his long history of running into the law and spending time in prison. He is one of the most notable aspiring artists in the game and is helping to put Austin Texas on the map. His partner, Southside Fresh utilizes a more aggressive, lyrical style. Fresh shows that he is a force to reckon with in the rap game. Both stand out as impressive solo artists, but when they come together, all bets are off.. For more info on UntamedClick visit their official Facebook fan page .
About Coast 2 Coast Mixtapes:
Coast 2 Coast Mixtapes are the most widely distributed mixtapes in the world, with over 100 million downloads/plays generated by over 300 volumes officially hosted by major artists. Coast 2 Coast has a solid reach in the new music industry with a digital magazine, DJ coalition, industry tips blog, yearly convention, and more. Coast 2 Coast Mixtapes represents a unique opportunity for artists of all urban genres, from major to indie. For more information, visit http://www.coast2coastmixtapes.com .
